    "description": "An exciting career opportunity awaits you at IL&FS Skills Ventures Solutions. We are on the lookout for a dedicated Instructional Designer to strengthen our Thane-based team.\n\nAbout IL&FS Skills Ventures Solutions:\nIL&FS Skills Ventures Solutions is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Contribute to school newsletter, blogs, and other publications\n• Monitor student progress and provide timely feedback\n• Design formative and summative assessments aligned to learning objectives\n• Conduct doubt-clearing sessions and remedial classes for weak students\n• Conduct parent-teacher meetings and update parents on student performance\n• Support students with special educational needs\n• Participate in teacher training and professional development programs\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Com / M.Com / MBA Finance\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Classroom Management\n• Proficiency in Student Assessment\n• Proficiency in LMS Platforms\n• Proficiency in Data Analysis\n• Proficiency in Mentoring\n• Proficiency in Pedagogy\n• Proficiency in Child Psychology\n• Proficiency in Content Creation\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Learning & development budget\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Thane, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with IL&FS Skills Ventures Solutions!",
